  "stem": "<p>Maria paid a total of <math><mo>$</mo><mn>248</mn></math> for a laptop by making a down payment of <math><mo>$</mo><mn>50</mn></math> plus <math><mi>n</mi></math> monthly payments of <math><mo>$</mo><mn>22</mn></math> each. Which of the following equations represents this situation?</p>",
