  "rationale": "<p>Choice A is correct. The monthly payments total <math><mn>22</mn><mi>n</mi></math>. Adding the down payment of 50 yields <math><mn>22</mn><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>50</mn></math>, and this equals the total 248.</p><p>Choices B, C, and D swap coefficients or operations and are incorrect.</p>",
